<template>
  <IonCard>
    <IonCardHeader>
      <IonCardTitle>{{ profile.displayName }}</IonCardTitle>
      <IonCardContent></IonCardContent>
    </IonCardHeader>
  </IonCard>
</template>

<script>
import {
  IonCard,
  IonCardHeader,
  IonCardSubtitle,
  IonCardTitle,
} from '@ionic/vue';

export default {
  name: "GroupItem",
  components: {IonCard, IonCardHeader, IonCardTitle,},
  props: {
    profile: Object,
  },
  methods: {
    showMeTheProfileName() {
      console.log(this.$props.profile.displayName)
    }
  },
  created() {
    this.$watch(
      () => {
        this.howMeTheProfileName()
      },
      // fetch the data when the view is created and the data is
      // already being observed
      { immediate: true }
    )
  },
}
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
